@Node "Inst" "Plug it in, turen it on and BANG your musilage"

     This is so easy my speccy could do it  <-- (Insert WoW here)

     1. Copy startup alpha to C:

     2. Make a directory called sequences in your S: directory

     3. Copy your Startup-Sequence to S:Sequences

     4. Make a new Startup-Sequence Containing the following

          C:StartupAlpha 
          EndCli

     5. Make some startups (see @{"Usage" Link "use" 0})

     6. Reboot and use the sucker

@Endnode

